# Videos
## What we do
We produce, film, edit and publish videos for social media campaigns, your website and online ads that capture viewers and hold their attention.

We use motion graphics (subtle animations and animated text) to excite your users and present information concisely. We also use them in the videos we produce to give the final product an elegant polish.

## How it benefits you 
Immortalise your event appearances, advertise products and explain their benefits in a way that engages people.

Video is the most engaging way to tell powerful stories that leverage viewers' emotions for maximum impact. If you can make your viewers feel something, they will be sure to remember you.

## Why we do it
We believe in the power of storytelling. We want to help companies we believe in tell their stories to the world.

# Social Media
## What we do
We design, produce and post consistent social media campaigns for you across platforms such as Instagram, Twitter and Youtube that will resonate with your target customers.

We produce content using our skills in photography, 3D rendering, videos and motion graphics.

We develop a recognisable tone of voice for your brand that represents its values and give it a personality.

We create tone of voice guidelines for you, so you can keep consistent across your website and other media.
## How it benefits you
Social platforms create a significant online presence for your brand and offer a place for you to engage with your customers, to create a community.

With 1-in-3 people in the world using social media, you can put your brand in front of a lot more people than traditional media allows.

Our content captures attention and holds it, displaying your brand in creative ways to separate it from your competition. Consistent, high quality content keeps people coming back.

A distinguished personality personifies your brand image, making it more relatable. When blended with a strategic content structure, it turns your brand into a lifestyle that customers will want to buy into.
## Why we do it
We believe that brands are better when they’re connected to their customers and we relish the challenge of converting brand values into a distinguished voice that stands out from the crowd.

# Websites
## What we do
We design, test and build you a beautiful website from scratch based on your users wants and business needs.

We don’t use templates, so you know that your users are getting a completely unique experience which will deepen your brand image.

We pull from our expertise in copywriting, video, motion graphics, 3D rendering and photography to create beautiful, on brand web content.

We create a unique engaging experience for your users by putting them first and conducting extensive user testing.
## How it benefits you
Provide a hub for your brand's online presence - a place for your customers to access information about your brand and products.

Offer bespoke features such as free sample ordering.

A unique experience distinguishes you from competitors, makes your brand memorable and converts users into customers.
## Why we do it
We want to share the value of online services with companies we love and flex our creative muscles in the process.
